<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses: </p>
<ul>
      <li>5: I know we have 5 fingers on each hand.</li>
      <li>6: I counted 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, and 6.</li>
      <li>7: I know one hand is 5 and then 6 and 7.</li>
    </ul>
